race.description: Yarradale Stud Ron Sayers Sprint Handicap (Bm66+)
race.comment: IMMORTAL BLISS (4) found one better two back before going under in a photo finish at Belmont last time out. Pike remains in the saddle and although he's drawn out, he has shown he can mow down his rivals from off the speed. Looks well placed in this event and can go one better. TAWKIN' JIBBERISH (12) was solid first-up at Belmont and is no doubt set for this event being out of the Fernie barn. He can settle much closer off the inside barrier this time around and she drops right down in weight. Can give her rivals something to chase. BONNIE LAD (10) boasts a strong record at this trip and is set to peak now third-up. Can feature in the finish. SIR DREAMALOT (6) needs some luck from the draw but has the class to feature.
